Class Album

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Album
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Album
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Album class is a model for albums. An album contains photos, name, and earliest/latest photo dates.
    Author:
    Vincent Phung, William McFarland
    See Also:
